of yours every damn year.

05:44.840 --> 05:46.280
Yeah? It's a tradition.

05:46.360 --> 05:49.080
[Lars] Tradition is great, Trond, but...

05:49.160 --> 05:53.400
[in English] It sure wasn't traditions
that brought the Olympics to this town.

05:53.480 --> 05:56.280
That was, you know...

05:56.360 --> 05:57.640
[in Norwegian]
Innovation.

05:58.960 --> 06:01.360
