[bartender in English]
There you go.

09:07.880 --> 09:10.760
[chuckles]

09:10.840 --> 09:13.600
What the fuck is this?

09:13.680 --> 09:15.800
What, are we a bunch of sorority girls?

09:15.880 --> 09:17.520
Bring out the real booze.

09:17.600 --> 09:19.760
[in Norwegian]
That's all the liquor that's left.

09:19.840 --> 09:22.680
But Roy said that there was
a delivery due yesterday.

09:22.760 --> 09:26.320
That's right, he called me
and said he was sick.

09:26.400 --> 09:30.040
[in English] And you were gonna inform me
of this exactly when?

09:47.640 --> 09:50.280
[in Norwegian] It's not like
I'm an exercise freak or nothing,

09:50.360 --> 09:53.560
but the doctor told me to train my back.

09:53.640 --> 09:56.320
In that case,
there's only one thing to do: Zumba.

09:57.960 --> 10:00.480
Is that like capoeira?

10:00.560 --> 10:02.480
You can have a free trial session,
if you want.

10:02.560 --> 10:05.440
Free? Now we're talking.

10:05.520 --> 10:09.800
Hello, all of you. My name is Arthur,
and together, we shall train Zumba.

10:09.880 --> 10:11.440
- Are you ready?
- [class] Yeah!

10:11.520 --> 10:12.960
[upbeat music playing over speakers]

10:13.040 --> 10:15.640
[Arthur]
Then we roll our hips, you guys!

10:15.720 --> 10:17.800
Sorry. I must have taken
a wrong turn somewhere.

10:17.880 --> 10:20.320
- I'm looking for Zumba.
