talking more like martial art.

10:22.160 --> 10:23.960
What? No, come on.

10:26.720 --> 10:28.120
[Arthur]
Are you having fun?

10:31.200 --> 10:32.920
That's good!

10:34.760 --> 10:36.200
Hey, what is your name?

10:36.280 --> 10:40.000
- Roy.
- You are good.

10:40.080 --> 10:43.920
Hip, ass, hip, ass, hip, ass.

10:44.000 --> 10:46.080
Yes, good.

10:46.160 --> 10:48.800
