10:48.880 --> 10:51.680
Look at Roy!
That's how it's done.

10:57.120 --> 10:58.640
You are so good.

10:58.720 --> 10:59.960
It's all those years riding a bike.

11:00.040 --> 11:01.760
Gotten used to dipping into turns.

11:01.840 --> 11:03.960
It's like oil for the hips.

11:16.000 --> 11:18.440
Yes? Why are you here?

11:18.520 --> 11:20.200
We talked to the guys
at the tattoo parlor.

11:20.280 --> 11:22.080
They said you went to pump some iron?

11:22.160 --> 11:25.440
Yeah, yeah.
Training is part of my rehab.

11:25.520 --> 11:27.680
It's been a lot of stress lately,
you know.

11:27.760 --> 11:29.960
- [in English] Stress.
- Yeah.

11:30.040 --> 11:33.120
I've been feeling stressful myself lately.

11:33.200 --> 11:35.080
Had to do with my last booze shipment,

11:35.160 --> 11:37.720
because it never showed up.

11:37.800 --> 11:39.920
[in Norwegian] Well, until I recover
from this slipped disc,

11:40.000 --> 11:42.720
I'm on full sick leave.

11:42.800 --> 11:45.040
[in English]
Are you losing your fucking mind?

11:45.120 --> 11:47.400
There's no Obamacare for bootleggers.

11:47.480 --> 11:49.240
- You deliver or you don't.
- Okay.

11:49.320 --> 11:50.960
[in Norwegian]
Okay, I'll make the delivery.

11:54.080 --> 11:58.280
But if it messes up my back,
you're paying for physio.

11:59.880 --> 12:01.280
[in English]
You got a deal.

12:01.360 --> 12:05.040
In fact, we'll throw in
a happy ending, huh?

12:05.120 --> 12:08.360
Just to put a smile back on that face.

12:08.440 --> 12:09.720
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

12:14.080 --> 12:15.880
[Lars in Norwegian]
A hundred meters from the top,

12:15.960 --> 12:18.600
I take off my boot and my sock

12:18.680 --> 12:20.880
and look down at my toe.

12:20.960 --> 12:22.480
It is pitch-black.

12:23.880 --> 12:26.520
Gangrene.

12:26.600 --> 12:30.120
I pull out my knife, cut the toe off

12:30.200 --> 12:34.880
and put it behind a rock
at 8,740 height meters.

12:35.640 --> 12:38.440
That's how it was when I launched
my clothing line, as well.

12:38.520 --> 12:42.040
Things looked dark, but I never gave up.

12:42.120 --> 12:45.280
Never give up.

12:47.680 --> 12:49.120
NEVER GIVE UP!

12:49.200 --> 12:50.560
[Lars]
Any questions?

12:50.640 --> 12:52.520
- Yeah?
- [man] I was just wondering about

12:52.600 --> 12:54.800
the entrepreneurial grant you run
along with Innovation Norway.

12:54.880 --> 12:57.880
- [Lars] Mm-hm.
- How much money can one apply for?

12:57.960 --> 12:59.520
[Lars chuckles]

12:59.600 --> 13:02.200
You sure cut to the chase.
I like that.

13:02.280 --> 13:03.520
"What's the money in this?"

13:10.480 --> 13:13.240
- Fine lecture.
- Good. Thank you.

13:13.320 --> 13:17.400
- This looks pretty exciting.
- Yeah?

13:17.480 --> 13:21.840
Why haven't you applied?
Flamingo is the perfect case.

13:21.920 --> 13:24.160
I'll mail some info to your boss.

13:24.240 --> 13:26.600
- Yeah.
- Mm-hm. Good.

13:30.640 --> 13:33.200
Wanna grab a beer at the bar?

13:33.280 --> 13:35.400
Talk about entrepreneurial stuff,

13:35.480 --> 13:38.440
both of us being entrepreneurs.

13:38.520 --> 13:41.600
Thanks, but, Torgeir,
I'm not exactly the beer-drinking kind.

13:41.680 --> 13:44.880
Oh, no. I am not really
a beer guy either.

13:44.960 --> 13:47.080
We'll see each other
at that lutefisk dinner anyway.

13:47.160 --> 13:50.040
Yes, we will. Looking forward to it.

13:50.120 --> 13:52.720
- You know what? So am I.
- Yeah.

13:52.800 --> 13:55.480
You sure you don't want a beer, though?

13:55.560 --> 13:57.480
My treat.

13:57.560 --> 13:58.960
Hey, you have learned something today.

14:00.600 --> 14:02.120
Never give up.

14:02.200 --> 14:04.000
Go out into this world.
Go get them.

14:04.080 --> 14:05.280
Yes, I will. Yes.

14:05.360 --> 14:06.880
- Reach for the top.
- Yes.

14:11.400 --> 14:13.520
[TV playing indistinctly]

14:20.880 --> 14:22.240
[groans]

14:37.440 --> 14:39.120
[Torgeir]
A beer for me.

14:56.400 --> 14:58.600
Got a snuff for me, as well?

14:58.680 --> 15:00.400
I only got loose.

15:00.480 --> 15:03.960
So? I don't eat candy with the wrapper on.

15:19.880 --> 15:23.480
Be careful so you don't swallow it,
it makes your stomach run.

15:23.560 --> 15:25.280
