15:59.480 --> 16:02.840
[The Woggles' "Big Beat Strong" playing]

16:25.920 --> 16:27.120
[sighs]

16:27.200 --> 16:29.080
Thank you.

16:29.160 --> 16:31.240
Feels damn good
to get back up on that horse.

16:32.960 --> 16:35.400
Did you just call me a horse?

16:35.480 --> 16:38.320
Aw, no. Just metaphorically.

16:38.400 --> 16:40.480
I've been struggling with a mental block

16:40.560 --> 16:42.360
when dealing with the ladies, you see.

16:49.680 --> 16:52.080
Jeez, did you rob a bank or what?

16:53.800 --> 16:55.640
I won a game of poker.

16:55.720 --> 16:57.760
I'm the kind of guy
who knows how to read people.

16:57.840 --> 16:59.440
But I guess you already noticed.

16:59.520 --> 17:01.240
Mm-hmm.

17:01.320 --> 17:04.280
And where does this card game go down?

17:04.360 --> 17:07.240
Down at the club I manage,
the Flamingo.

17:07.320 --> 17:10.520
I'd love to invite you,

17:10.600 --> 17:12.760
but it's sort of a guy thing.

17:12.840 --> 17:14.560
Mm-hmm.

17:16.400 --> 17:17.720
I see.

17:20.960 --> 17:22.520
Good night.

17:23.800 --> 17:25.280
Good night.

17:32.120 --> 17:34.400
You like to spoon?

17:34.480 --> 17:35.960
No.

17:36.040 --> 17:38.520
Oh.

17:51.920 --> 17:57.680
Today, I'm dressed as one of the most
beautiful things in nature: a sperm cell.

17:58.960 --> 18:05.280
That is because sperm is
still taboo in many cultures.

18:05.360 --> 18:09.440
It is to remove the taboo.

18:09.520 --> 18:12.440
Just push it away.

18:14.080 --> 18:18.520
We have a big problem in this community.

18:18.600 --> 18:22.640
We have far too few sperm donors
with non-western backgrounds.

18:24.000 --> 18:26.080
This is Ali from NRK Oppland.

18:26.160 --> 18:28.600
