without any luck.

18:32.840 --> 18:36.880
We went there to the fertility clinic,

18:36.960 --> 18:39.640
intending to make a sunshine story
about artificial insemination.

18:39.720 --> 18:41.800
But it didn't turn out a sunshine story,
did it, Ali?

18:43.280 --> 18:45.800
No.

18:45.880 --> 18:48.120
They had no biological material
of my kind.

18:48.200 --> 18:49.640
[in English]
Yo, what is he talking about?

18:49.720 --> 18:52.240
- His boys, they can't swim.
- Oh. [chuckles]

18:52.320 --> 18:54.320
[shushing]

18:54.400 --> 18:58.000
[in Norwegian] I know this might be
awkward for you.

18:58.080 --> 18:59.680
But we're in Norway now.

18:59.760 --> 19:04.960
Here, those who have plenty
share with those who have little,

19:05.040 --> 19:06.520
even when it comes to sperm.

19:06.600 --> 19:10.840
All that remains is signing up with Siri,
the nice girl over there. Hi, Siri.

19:10.920 --> 19:13.400
- [Siri] Hello.
- [Jan] Yes, Siri is her name.

19:22.160 --> 19:25.240
Not everyone has adjusted to the Norwegian
way of thinking, like you have.

19:25.400 --> 19:26.880
- Hey, Jan.
- Yes?

19:26.960 --> 19:29.320
- When do I get my room?
- Room?

19:29.400 --> 19:33.960
Yes. It says that the winner
gets a single room.

19:34.040 --> 19:37.680
And I have used
all of my calling card on this.

19:37.760 --> 19:40.360
This is something
we can talk about later. Yes.

19:42.720 --> 19:46.600
"The chairman of the Flamingo group
is nominated for the Flame Award."

19:46.680 --> 19:49.360
Have you cheated with the voting?

19:51.760 --> 19:55.920
Remember, you're visiting
as a private person, not a reporter.

19:56.840 --> 19:58.560
[laughs]

20:03.160 --> 20:04.920
[sighs]

20:05.000 --> 20:06.720
[elevator dings]

20:21.640 --> 20:23.080
Hello?

20:27.240 --> 20:28.640
Hello?

