[mutters]

20:35.480 --> 20:37.480
[machine whirring]

20:37.560 --> 20:39.680
[in English]
Where's your brother?

20:39.760 --> 20:42.840
[in Norwegian] I don't fucking know.
We were having tacos yesterday,

20:42.920 --> 20:46.360
but he didn't show.
I had to eat the whole thing myself.

20:50.720 --> 20:52.880
[in English]
Hello, boys.

20:52.960 --> 20:56.640
[Johnny] Look who finally showed up.
Where were you last night?

20:56.720 --> 20:59.240
[in Norwegian] I guess you can say
I was held up.

20:59.320 --> 21:02.920
I know that grin.
Did you score last night?

21:03.000 --> 21:05.160
[in English]
"A gentleman never tells."

21:05.240 --> 21:06.680
[in Norwegian]
Ain't that how the saying goes?

21:06.760 --> 21:09.200
Congratulations, Torgeir.
Who's the lucky guy?

21:09.280 --> 21:11.360
[all laugh]

21:11.440 --> 21:13.480
[Torgeir]
She was actually a real piece.

21:13.560 --> 21:16.040
She asked me for a snuff,
and before you knew it,

21:16.120 --> 21:18.160
