40:11.800 --> 40:13.520
[in Norwegian]
Then what happens with the new CEO?

40:13.600 --> 40:16.920
[in English]
That's why I'm here. I want you back.

40:18.520 --> 40:21.120
[in English] Ah. I don't know.

40:25.800 --> 40:28.440
I got Italian blood.

40:28.520 --> 40:31.320
Sometimes I get a little...

40:31.400 --> 40:33.360
...overenthusiastic.

40:34.960 --> 40:39.040
We started that club together,

40:39.120 --> 40:41.840
and I'm gonna keep it that way.

40:41.920 --> 40:43.640
You gonna make me beg?

40:45.760 --> 40:47.160
No.

40:49.040 --> 40:51.400
To tell you the truth,

40:51.480 --> 40:53.320
I really want the job back.

40:53.400 --> 40:55.480
It's the best job
I've ever had in my life.

40:55.560 --> 40:58.480
[chuckles] Right.

40:58.560 --> 41:00.640
What other jobs have you had?

41:02.440 --> 41:04.720
I'm fucking with you.
Welcome back.

41:04.800 --> 41:07.840
You dirty rat.
You nearly got me.

41:07.920 --> 41:09.520
This far.

41:09.600 --> 41:11.920
So, what are we watching?

41:12.000 --> 41:13.920
Goodfellas  starts after this.

41:14.000 --> 41:17.800
Oh, yeah? What was the name
of Joe Pesci's character again?

41:17.880 --> 41:20.360
Tommy DeVito.
Best role in his life.

41:20.440 --> 41:22.280
That's my partner.

41:26.560 --> 41:32.080
[in Norwegian] There is one thing...
I need to tell you.

41:32.280 --> 41:35.640
[in English]
You know the lady I, uh, banged?

41:37.080 --> 41:39.520
It was the sheriff.

41:39.600 --> 41:43.200
- Fuck.
- But you gotta believe me, I didn't know.

41:43.320 --> 41:46.600
If she was a cop, I would never have
anything to do with her.

41:46.680 --> 41:49.360
[in Norwegian] I only thought
she was interested in cards--

41:49.440 --> 41:51.360
[in English]
Do me a favor.

41:51.440 --> 41:53.360
- Stop talking.
- Yeah.

41:53.440 --> 41:55.480
You're making me regret
taking you back already.

41:55.560 --> 41:57.960
I'll stop talking right away.

41:58.040 --> 41:59.880
[sighs]

42:01.240 --> 42:04.080
[Bing Bang's "Epic Scrap Metal" playing]

42:36.360 --> 42:38.280
[Johnny]
Sorry, pal, we're closed.

42:38.360 --> 42:41.640
- Good. Then we can talk.
- [chuckles]

42:41.720 --> 42:44.720
I smell a cop.
Tell me I'm wrong.

42:44.800 --> 42:48.640
PST, actually,
the Norwegian Homeland Security.

42:49.640 --> 42:52.120
Our happy hour's been
a little crazy lately,

42:52.200 --> 42:54.960
but I didn't think we were
a national security threat.

42:55.040 --> 42:58.680
This isn't about your club.
Can we talk in private?

43:00.720 --> 43:04.040
Eight days ago,
a bank vault was robbed in Oslo.

43:04.120 --> 43:07.800
The press is calling it
the "Bieber Bank Heist."

43:07.880 --> 43:09.680
I tell you what.

43:09.760 --> 43:13.600
When guys start pulling heists
wearing Tony Bennett masks,

43:13.680 --> 43:15.440
you come see me.

43:17.800 --> 43:21.040
You're not a suspect.
The fact is that

43:21.120 --> 43:23.560
one of the bank boxes that got robbed, uh,

43:23.640 --> 43:28.000
contained some, uh, sensitive information.

43:28.080 --> 43:29.960
And I need your help to get it back.

43:30.040 --> 43:33.120
Well, sorry, pal.
But unless you need catering,

43:33.200 --> 43:34.920
there's nothing I can do for you.

43:35.000 --> 43:38.120
Some of the information
that got lost is, uh...

43:39.880 --> 43:42.320
...is about you, Mr. Tagliano.

43:45.440 --> 43:48.920
- Come again?
- You heard me.

43:49.000 --> 43:51.080
Frank Tagliano?

43:53.880 --> 43:55.720
All right.

43:55.800 --> 43:59.120
You have my complete attention.

43:59.200 --> 44:02.720
[The Impressions' "Fool for You" playing]
